Class Mover

  • java.lang.Object
    • Mover
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Fish, Hook, Trash

    public class Mover
extends java.lang.Object
    This represents all the moving objects on the screen at a time and holds their attributes of position, speed, and direction.
